    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, rip your<strong> ciabatta[s]</strong> into large, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Cut your <strong>cherry tomatoes </strong>in half</p><p>Cut your <strong>cucumber</strong> in half lengthways, then slice finely</p><p>Peel and grate your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
