    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>lettuce</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper and roughly shred</p><p>Chop your <strong>basil</strong> roughly, including the stalks</p><p>Chop your <strong>black olives </strong>in half</p><p>Drain your <strong>mozzarella</strong>, then pat and squeeze as much liquid out as you can with kitchen paper</p><p>Tear the <strong>drained</strong> <strong>mozzarella</strong> into rough, bite-sized pieces</p>",
