    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the veg is tender, remove the tray[s] from the oven and top with the <strong>torn</strong> <strong>ciabatta</strong></p><p>Drizzle with a little <strong>olive</strong> <strong>oil</strong>, then return the tray[s] to the oven for a further 5-6 min or until golden and crisp</p>",
