    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>red wine vinegar</strong> in a large bowl with the <strong>grated</strong> <strong>garlic </strong>and a pinch <strong>salt</strong>, <strong>pepper</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Gradually whisk in a generous drizzle of <strong>olive</strong> <strong>oil</strong> – this is your <strong>dressing</strong></p>",
