    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>torn</strong> <strong>lettuce</strong> and <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>cucumber</strong> to the bowl of dressing with the <strong>halved</strong> <strong>cherry</strong> <strong>tomatoes</strong>, <strong>halved</strong> <strong>olives</strong> and <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>basil </strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>salad</strong></p>",
