    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>roast</strong> <strong>potatoes</strong>, <strong>red onion wedges </strong>and<strong> croutons </strong>topped with the <strong>salad</strong> and <strong>torn mozzarella </strong>– this is your <strong>warm panzanella salad with mozzarella</strong></p><p>Drizzle with <strong>olive</strong> <strong>oil</strong> and season with a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
